      • of

        static java.util.concurrent.CompletableFuture<User> of​(long id)
        Gets a user from only an ID. This method requires to be run from a Bot-Own Thread, see ThreadPool.isBotOwnThread(). This method must only be invoked from "bot-own" threads.
        Parameters:
        id - The ID to get a user for.
        Returns:
        A future to contain a user with the given id.
        Throws:
        java.lang.IllegalCallerException - If the current thread does not belong to any Discord object.
